{"tid":2791,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"你地當年有冇人睇過中國一套叫大鬧天宮嘅動畫？","createTime":"2016-11-26T02:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T15:17:54.000Z","uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c67f073ae37058b380dfdc6c48689662d38bf26f","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:24:22.000Z","msg":"係文革前後嘅作品，動畫中嘅參與者都被鬥過，成套作品啲前期同手稿都被燒毀，估唔到中國會有啲咁高水準嘅野，連今時今日啲外國鬼佬都睇到呆曬，迪士尼講緊二十年後先有相當水準嘅作品出現，獅子王等等<br />\n雖然我唔係大中華膠，但我有時諗今日嘅中國如果冇發生過文革，會有幾多高質素作品出現<br />\n<br />\n附上link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kyZ4kvJl1jY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkyZ4kvJl1jY&d=J%2FdDR1h%2FRUzdpwiA6Y8oy8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=0bc886db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kyZ4kvJl1jY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/102135_6b2f2d9951cd12467d8aee0179cff178.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F102135_6b2f2d9951cd12467d8aee0179cff178.jpg&h=6c5c2bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/102137_8760dfdef7fd5ea7e01d76c166c41dba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F102137_8760dfdef7fd5ea7e01d76c166c41dba.jpg&h=1f80ce0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/102138_7a7c8d879db06f15c3779c6925b3f164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F102138_7a7c8d879db06f15c3779c6925b3f164.jpg&h=dc0f09dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmavN7LQtd5XrBBq8AeWrU2JRCTVPwbYAzg1og8ZnBAg1x?filename=D521kq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD521kq.jpg&h=d3fe845f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWNTmRzZRshQAVwZir9eBKRxNhYjSwxm8r9mLc2JgtQeg?filename=9cm2Z0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cm2Z0.jpg&h=216ce34a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWiCetMbppEaiJBFr9UgHr5F3ZLKe2m91uMuJj5sbtgGL?filename=563vg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F563vg9.jpg&h=62a61afb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abbcdcd09528a6bd119c2f4eb6abbc8cd6ac7f94","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:39:20.000Z","msg":"高質野冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb3d28672b3062b771b11a279f5c3914a4f7ed5","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"值得一提係玉皇大帝有粒墨係下巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有點諷刺意味"},{"pid":"5ad765564eaaa338cbab69f777a438ffe60b006d","tid":2791,"uid":3439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"係咪因為用水墨畫黎做動畫而出名嗰套？"},{"pid":"9b149f45e6ae1727c83da7f96c79b11243e200d8","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪因為用水墨畫黎做動畫而出名嗰套？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個套叫蝌蚪找媽媽，呢套神奇在到今時今日，都冇人知點解水墨畫會控制到連貫成動畫，連鬼佬啲動畫大師都r曬頭<br />\n其實文革前中國文化真係好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fa05e25d7947d0fb091956bc190b65bdab5ccf","tid":2791,"uid":338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"九十年代有線兒童台做過<br />\n係幾好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec1a0b2d42d7b3e971848cf0d544f2add6fcb1b","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪因為用水墨畫黎做動畫而出名嗰套？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個套叫蝌蚪找媽媽，呢套神奇在到今時今日，都冇人知點解水墨畫會控制到連貫成動畫，連鬼佬啲動畫大師都r曬頭<br />\n其實文革前中國文化真係好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文革後所有野被燒毀，好多文化人都被鬥死，冇紀錄保存到，所以都冇辦法重現呢樣技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88538d35ca48e3042014daa89dcdc1b641bdc540","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九十年代有線兒童台做過<br />\n係幾好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇嘅係上集加不完整嘅下集<br />\n當年係被禁作品，下集好似過左好多年先公開完整版"},{"pid":"910f6fb9df3e142193aa1237dd01aa88cb71ec2b","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:19:52.000Z","msg":"推比更多人睇"},{"pid":"a4c62f683da493ba9f6e3af1a2282399609cf320","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa69fc54f66107b83fa616db82c025eb731ecb7","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4fe4a2ca493d50553cb6991976daae0f5820e9","tid":2791,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac53e0ea592f93d4e43c388dc49390162650c0f","tid":2791,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}